## ðŸ”¥ **SAMUEWE o5-Max â€“ Dynamic OnTick Engine (Full Upgrade)**

**Replace your main OnTick with this version.**
*(Iâ€™m leaving helper functions, drawing, and trade execution as-is, but I can fill those in too if you want)*

